data.description: Discover the charm of this Lake Placid gem! Nestled in the heart of town, this property boasts 1.08 acres (47,226 sq ft) of lush landscape. The spacious backyard is adorned with fruitful trees, offering a serene retreat. Inside, find 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a generous living room. A unique touch is the Koi pond in the great room and a fountain to accentuate, adding tranquility to the living space. The property alo features an office space and 2 sheds with electricity provision, enhancing its practicality. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home!
